如果連先姦後殺未成年少女都獲得特赦,我就唔明追究警暴實際內容係咩"},{"pid":"0a025305bcd5011055875f8e5b1abd36ff75c8b7","tid":1794994,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c22730a0991c569465ecff7c8e6f07686824762","tid":1794994,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/黎智英/daily/article/20191222/20829417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191222%2F20829417%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=a57b1d23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191222%2F20829417%2F&h=c79a4ee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/黎智英/daily/article/20191222/20829417/</a><br />\n<br />\n覺得我係五毛 mon po狗可以起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日想搞大台 要人聽從你泛民支笛 <br />\n請你好好記住能夠走到今日係全靠冇大台 兄弟爬山呢個信念 冇人可以指揮任何人抗爭<br />\n我地可以推你上嚟 一樣可以拉返你落嚟 <br />\n你泛民夠膽割前線 唔好真係以為你仲有民主飯食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們要警惕的是不良份子的滲透破壞。例如最近警方檢獲的手槍和子彈，兩枚炸彈和黑衣人在終審法院門前扔汽油彈縱火等，我懷疑都是想將我們運動的暴力擴大，破壞我們運動的滲透者所為。這些滲透者聽說是有中國背影，想在港製造麻煩給習帝的權鬥對手所為。他們想利用我們的運動作為中共權鬥的彈藥，我們不能中計。那天跟陳日君樞機談起，他說要避免滲透，勇武派是時候組織領袖團隊，有了領袖團隊便有了原則和勇武的底線，滲透者的過激行動便輕易被揭發，因而想利用我們的運動作為權鬥的彈藥就難以得逞。勇武的手足們，請考慮一下陳樞機的意見。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T21:40:05.000Z","msg":"其實鬼係可以唔入你個團隊然後繼續做嘢屈你，洗鬼入你個on9團隊咩！"},{"pid":"8e25644bee9fadbc67f6abe69d71a4e22633c469","tid":1794994,"uid":7760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"無一個組織可以騎劫場運動<br />\n你話我熱狗五毛我都係咁講"},{"pid":"8fd47e4a7587d1f94d1077a0b8a54e1b1e0b19de","tid":1794994,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193799dd5f0adeae97ef89303dcfce7087b104dd","tid":1794994,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:31:29.000Z","msg":"你地班港獨狗原來收左大陸錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係我講嫁<br />\n<br />\n還有聽說一些鼓吹港獨的知名人士，都是習帝權鬥對手促使，想在香港製造大災難，逼中共派解放軍入城鎮壓，掀起自由世界對中國經濟和政治制裁，給今日面對四面楚歌危機四伏之際的習帝添麻煩，我們必須小心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc0c458cabe778d9463211ada60caccdad7d043","tid":1794994,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tx0z01X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftx0z01X.jpg&h=9954a5c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed8fb5a98f0bb476a4a2f0fa12035204ca01fde2","tid":1794994,"uid":191612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"成個連登都泛民打手點會推得郁個po 唉"},{"pid":"7ca16b96722b9835f22dad9820c1c2428b83c24